CHILDPROFILE EXTENSION (app/src/types.ts):
Add to the ChildProfile interface (additive, optional, non-breaking):
  interests?: string[];
  // COPPA note: interests[] is child-associated data. arbor-safety COPPA review required on write path.
  // No interest is ever surfaced as a developmental verdict or diagnostic signal.
  // Default: undefined (treated as [] by all consumers for backward compat).

PLAYACTIVITY EXTENSION (app/src/playbank/content.ts):
Add to PlayActivity interface:
  themeableContextSlot?: boolean;
  // true = the object/context in this activity can be substituted with a child interest
  //        without changing the developmental target, observable signals, or parent prompts.
  // false or undefined = not substitutable (the activity's physical objects are load-bearing
  //                      to the developmental purpose, e.g. a calm-down jar relies on the jar).
  // Authoring guideline: set true when the activity description contains a generic object
  //   (ball, block, toy) that could be any child-chosen object without changing the skill being practiced.
  // Examples: true for turn-taking-tower (blocks -> dinosaurs), sock-basketball (socks -> any soft toy).
  //           false for calm-down-jar (the jar + glitter are the sensory tool), kitchen-band (pots are the instrument).

PLAYSELECTCONTEXT EXTENSION (app/src/playbank/select.ts):
Add to PlaySelectContext:
  interests?: string[];
  // Child's recorded interest array. Used to apply interestBoost multiplier
  // to themeable activities. Empty/undefined = no boost applied.

SCOREDACTIVITY EXTENSION (app/src/playbank/select.ts):
Extend reason union:
  reason: 'concern-match' | 'stage-match' | 'interest-match';
  // 'interest-match': activity is themeable AND at least one interest matches.
  //   The existing 'concern-match' rank takes priority: if an activity is both
  //   interest-matched and concern-matched, reason = 'concern-match'.
  //   interest-match fires only when concern-match does not.

RANKDAILYPLAY SCORING CHANGE (app/src/playbank/select.ts):
In the existing score formula:
  const score = bandScore * concernBoost * novelty + jitter(activity.id, daySeed) * 0.05;
Change to:
  const interestBoost = (activity.themeableContextSlot && (ctx.interests?.length ?? 0) > 0) ? 1.25 : 1;
  const score = bandScore * concernBoost * novelty * interestBoost + jitter(activity.id, daySeed) * 0.05;
The 1.25x multiplier is conservative (lower than the existing 1.8x concernBoost) so concern-match activities are not displaced by interest-only activities.

